name: StarCraft 2 | Protoss
description:
This LoRA is trained with 14 images, varying from cosplays to fan arts, of StarCraft 2 Protoss.

Simply load up your favorite model and use <lora:starcraft2protoss:1> for this lora to take effect!

This LoRA was trained using SD 1.5 and therefore may not work with all models!

For Epoch Version use <lora:starcraft2protoss-000010:1> or <lora:starcraft2protoss-000020:1>

For early access and custom LoRA's consider joining my patreon! https://patreon.com/Crazygirlashleyy

Preview Images made using:
CrazyGirlAshley-Mix-2
